364 class BattleExperienceEvent : public BasicEvent
365 {
366 public:
367  static uint32 const ExperiencedSpells[5];
368  static uint32 const ExperiencedTimes[5];
369 
370  BattleExperienceEvent(Creature* creature) : _creature(creature), _level(0) { }
371 
372  bool Execute(uint64 timer, uint32 /*diff*/) override
373  {
374  if (!_creature->IsAlive())
375  return true;
376 
377  _creature->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(ExperiencedSpells[_level]);
378  ++_level;
379 
380  _creature->CastSpell(_creature, ExperiencedSpells[_level], true);
381  if (_level < (_creature->GetMap()->IsHeroic() ? 4 : 3))
382  {
383  _creature->m_Events.AddEvent(this, timer + ExperiencedTimes[_level]);
384  return false;
385  }
386 
387  return true;
388  }
389 
390 private:
391  Creature* _creature;
392  int32 _level;
393 };

398 class PassengerController
399 {
400 public:
401  PassengerController()
402  {
403  ResetSlots(TEAM_HORDE, nullptr);
404  }
405 
406  void ResetSlots(TeamId teamId, MotionTransport* t)
407  {
408  _transport = t;
409 
410  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_SLOTS; ++i)
411  {
412  _controlledSlots[i].Clear();
413  _respawnCooldowns[i] = time_t(0);
414  }
415 
416  _spawnPoint = teamId == TEAM_HORDE ? &OrgrimsHammerAddsSpawnPos : &SkybreakerAddsSpawnPos;
417  _slotInfo = teamId == TEAM_HORDE ? OrgrimsHammerSlotInfo : SkybreakerSlotInfo;
418  }
419 
420  bool SummonCreatures(Creature* summoner, PassengerSlots first, PassengerSlots last)
421  {
422  if (!_transport)
423  return false;
424 
425  bool summoned = false;
426  time_t now = time(nullptr);
427  for (int32 i = first; i <= last; ++i)
428  {
429  if (_respawnCooldowns[i] > now)
430  continue;
431 
432  if (_controlledSlots[i])
433  {
434  Creature* current = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*_transport, _controlledSlots[i]);
435  if (current && current->IsAlive())
436  continue;
437  }
438 
439  Position spawnPos = SelectSpawnPoint();
440  if (Creature* passenger = summoner->SummonCreature(_slotInfo[i].Entry, spawnPos, TEMPSUMMON_CORPSE_TIMED_DESPAWN, 15000))
441  {
442  if (!passenger->GetTransport())
443  _transport->AddPassenger(passenger, true);
444  passenger->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_ID, 49576, true); // death grip
445 
446  if (i >= SLOT_MAGE_1 && i <= SLOT_MORTAR_4) // only these npcs are pooled
447  {
448  _controlledSlots[i] = passenger->GetGUID();
449  _respawnCooldowns[i] = time_t(0);
450  }
451  passenger->AI()->SetData(ACTION_SET_SLOT, i);
452  summoned = true;
453  }
454  }
455 
456  return summoned;
457  }
458 
459  void ClearSlot(PassengerSlots slot)
460  {
461  _controlledSlots[slot].Clear();
462  _respawnCooldowns[slot] = time(nullptr) + _slotInfo[slot].Cooldown;
463  }
464 
465 private:
466  Position SelectSpawnPoint() const
467  {
468  float angle = frand(-M_PI * 0.5f, M_PI * 0.5f);
469  Position newPos;
470  newPos.m_positionX = _spawnPoint->GetPositionX() + 2.0f * std::cos(angle);
471  newPos.m_positionY = _spawnPoint->GetPositionY() + 2.0f * std::sin(angle);
472  newPos.m_positionZ = _spawnPoint->GetPositionZ();
473  newPos.SetOrientation(_spawnPoint->GetOrientation());
474  _transport->CalculatePassengerPosition(newPos.m_positionX, newPos.m_positionY, newPos.m_positionZ, &(newPos.m_orientation));
475  return newPos;
476  }
477 
478  ObjectGuid _controlledSlots[MAX_SLOTS];
479  time_t _respawnCooldowns[MAX_SLOTS];
480  MotionTransport* _transport;
481  Position const* _spawnPoint;
482  SlotInfo const* _slotInfo;
483 };

485 class DelayedMovementEvent : public BasicEvent
486 {
487 public:
488  DelayedMovementEvent(Creature* owner, Position const& dest) : _owner(owner), _dest(dest) { }
489 
490  bool Execute(uint64, uint32) override
491  {
492  if (!_owner->IsAlive() || !_owner->GetTransport())
493  return true;
494 
495  float x, y, z, o;
496  _dest.GetPosition(x, y, z, o);
497  _owner->GetTransport()->CalculatePassengerPosition(x, y, z, &o);
498  _owner->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(EVENT_CHARGE_PREPATH, x, y, z, false);
499  return true;
500  }
501 
502 private:
503  Creature* _owner;
504  Position const& _dest;
505 };

507 class ResetEncounterEvent : public BasicEvent
508 {
509 public:
510  ResetEncounterEvent(Unit* caster, uint32 spellId, ObjectGuid otherTransport) : _caster(caster), _spellId(spellId), _otherTransport(otherTransport) { }
511 
512  bool Execute(uint64, uint32) override
513  {
514  _caster->CastSpell(_caster, _spellId, true);
515  _caster->GetTransport()->ToMotionTransport()->UnloadNonStaticPassengers();
516  _caster->GetTransport()->AddObjectToRemoveList();
517 
518  if (Transport* transport = ObjectAccessor::GetTransport(*_caster, _otherTransport))
519  {
520  transport->ToMotionTransport()->UnloadNonStaticPassengers();
521  transport->AddObjectToRemoveList();
